Dialogs.Dialog: ▲主人公＊▲. I'm surprised to see you in such a place.
I'm surprised too... Are you watching the fountain?
It's a little worrisome. I'm just looking at the flow of water.
Huh... the flow of water. ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s point of view is interesting.
▲主人公＊▲. Are you taking a walk?
Well, you can say that. ▲高嶺＊＊▲ too?
That so. This is a great walk spot.
Yes, the view is good and it feels good.
If I can see you, why don't I always try to pass here when I take a walk?
I like that. Should I do the same?
Huh. What are you doing here,▲高嶺＊＊▲?
▲主人公＊▲. Emmm... I haven't done anything.
If you feel a little tired, you should come here. Isn't it important to take a break?
A break, huh... Then, I'll also take a break.
Whassup, what a coincidence. Did you watch a movie?
No, I came to get a flyer for the upcoming movie.
I'm looking forward to it. Then, why don't we come to see this together?
I'm sorry, I promised to see it with my friends...
Haha, I was denied. If you have a previous compromise, I can't help it.
I worried in vain... We can date anytime.
▲高嶺＊＊▲? I didn't see you in such a place.
Alone? You could have invited me...
It's nothing. I have an errand, so I'll see you later.
Whassup, such a coincidence. What are you doing?
Since I came here, I wonder what kind of movie I'm seeing. I don't have time to watch it yet.
There is a screening schedule at the entrance. Do you have enough time to see it?
It was a voluntary practice, so I'm going home now.
I see, my timing was off.
Just kidding. Then, do your best.
（Maybe I didn't get the timing right?）
I'm sorry. I didn't expected to see you.
Didn't you want to meet me?
That's not true... I'm here, but I wanted to keep it secret.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Did you go to the sports center?
I feel a little heavy in the mornings. So I come to be sure.
Yes, it was just a matter of feelings. Manaka is in great shape today.
I'm lucky to see you. So, let's go together.
I've finished shopping already, and I have to go home...
Somehow I understand, I'm out of luck.
Ah, it was you... Fufu, I'm so surprised that I laugh.
Haha. It certainly makes me laugh times like this.
Indeed. You must mean by accident. What do you want to eat, curry or stew tonight?
Thank you, I was wondering which one to choose. I'll have curry tonight. See you, Mama is waiting.
（Takane's menu... I though it would be for me）
There are quite a few people.
Oh,▲高嶺＊＊▲. Look like it's exciting, doesn't it? Did you come to see it?
I saw it while taking a walk. I have to get back.
I hope we can come together next time. See ya.
▲主人公＊▲. Isn't it great to see you here?
I see. I don't think I'm doing anything interesting.
Haha, I was inviting▲高嶺＊＊▲ from the beginning.
Oh,▲高嶺＊＊▲. Are you going home now?
I'm not going back yet. Yes, if you came a little earlier...
I can meet you anytime... but, I'm a little disappointed.
Hey, what kind of games do you play?
You're going to the arcade. Don't be too late, will you?
I understand. How about ▲高嶺＊＊▲ and I go together.
I have to go back home. See ya.
Did you look into the arcade? I thought I was going to enter alone.
That sort of thing... that's right, I was on an errant.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲ is not good at acting...）
Were you in the arcade now?
That so. Hey, let's play together!
I'm sorry, I'm being asked to use it now.
Then it's not possible. Well, let's go together again.
That's right, with Papa and Mama. Are you over there?
▲主人公＊▲. Just in the right place.
Hey, what's the difference between this shelf and that one?
Emm... Ah, there's a catalog. Wait a minute...
Thank you. I'm a little bad at this kind of thing...
I knew it▲高嶺＊＊▲. I can hear your voice.
What... Well, I have to change my voice.
（Even if this is not the case...）
Oh, I found my boyfriend... I'm kidding.
Emm... I wonder what should I do. I'm at a loss.
Can you listen to it? Then I would like to listen too.
Alright, so if you like it,▲高嶺＊＊▲, you may buy it.
What's wrong, do you like the piano?
Well... I wonder about that.▲高嶺＊＊▲, mentioned you liked it.
（I know that melody, but I can't remember the name of the song）
That bag, did you buy something?
（I wonder what you bought... I shouldn't worry）
Such a coincidence. Did you come to do some shopping?
I'm not trying to buy anything in particular.
That so. It's just fun here.
I see... I wanted to go out with you, but I have to go back.
I see, it's a pitty. I'll come again next time.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, did you have an errant here?
Yup. But there were a lot of things and I ended overwhelmed.
I see,▲高嶺＊＊▲ what kind of things interest you?
Not me. My aunt was looking for a present for her friend's child, so I'm doing some research.
Are you even doing it? I want to help you.
Really? Thank you so much for helping me.
You don't have to be so surprised...
You just happened to pass by here... it's true?
Do you want to go to this shop by any chance?
Hmm... I wonder if there's someone you're look for.
Eh! That's not true! I just want a cup of tea!
... You don't have anything to do, do you?
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Did you take a peel at this shop now?
... Hey, do you think that uniform is cute?
Maid clothes? Well yeah, they're... cute, aren't they?
If you work part-time here, you can wear them.
It's cute, but I don't want you to show it to other guys...
... Why can you say such a thing so honestly?
Oh,▲高嶺＊＊▲? It's rare to meet you in a place like this.
I come occasionally. I like the shrine because it has a unique atmosphere.
Certainly. Don't you feel your back stretched out.
Yes, yes, I'm going to do it.
I think I'll draw my fortune...
Oh,▲高嶺＊＊▲. It's no coincidence we met at this time!
So why don't we draw our fortune together?
Hmm... no. I want to make it a day to pay a proper visit. I have some urgent business to do.
▲主人公＊▲. It's surprising to see you at such place.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, what are you doing? Your wishes?
In this place, yes. However, the contents of my wishes are secret.
Eh, I want to hear them.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Don't meet me in such an unexpected place.
I want to go out with you, but I have an errand... I think it's best to practice alone. Work hard.
I'm bowling now. What to do it together?
I'm sorry. There's a place I have to go now.
I see. If you have an errand, I can't do anything.
Good luck with your bowling. Fight!
▲高嶺＊＊▲! Such a coincidence. Were you bowling?
With some friends. Here, look at the score table.
I did my best. I can't lose against you, can I? I'm keeping my friends waiting, so I'll go.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Did you go to karaoke?
Yeah, with some friends from my class.
I see, I wish you had invited me too.
It's not possible. There are things only girls can hear.
▲高嶺＊＊▲? Did you go to karaoke?
Alone? Ah, maybe you were practicing?
Geez... Don't say things like that.
（I wonder what I should do today...）
Would you like to have our next date here?
Fufu, it's a coincidence. I like your surprised face.
（I don't want you to see my face that much...）
Not really.▲高嶺＊＊▲, are you training in this park?
Sometimes. This is just the right place for a jogging goal.
Huh... a goal, in here. Sounds good.
Right? Tanake's goal. I feel like that.
Oh, hello. Are you taking a walk?
Yes, I'm taking a walk with the dog of my neighbor's child.
A walk over here. Huh, what about the dog?
I saw you, so I left it over there. See ya.
▲主人公＊▲. What are you doing in such a place?
Maybe... tennis practice? Playing with a ball is prohibited here.
No, no. Today I'm... taking a walk.
（It's not a preview for a date...）
Yes, for some tea. And you ▲高嶺＊＊▲?
I changed my mind. Sometimes I think it's good to study outside of my room.
I understand. So, what are the results?
It might be a little wrong. I'll go home and continue.
Yeah, I come here sometimes when I'm alone.
I wish you had invited me.
I'm sorry. Then, why don't we go now?
I have someting else to do.
...If that's the case, I can't even ask you out.
Even so, I wanted you to speak to me.
▲主人公＊▲. Actually, I asked for a takeout.
Oh, you've grown up, haven't you?
Oh you, don't think other people are like children.
Haha, sorry. By the way, are you free now?
No, I have to go home. Sorry.
Oh,▲高嶺＊＊▲. What are you doing?
I'm shopping with my family. I came after you when I saw you.
Is that a bother? That's bad.
No. It's sad that you didn't talk to me when I was able to see you. See you.
Whassup. I was just about to enter this store.
How about it▲高嶺＊＊▲, we should enter together.
Um, Papa is waiting over there... Can 3 people come in?
▲主人公＊▲. Are you going to have a meal?
Hello,▲高嶺＊＊▲. Yeah, something like that.
When you live alone, you can eat food when you want and when you like. That's amazing.
▲主人公＊▲. Are you going to dine here?
Do you like the food here? I see...
I wonder if I can make it. Fufu.
I've heard about this store in TV.
I thought I would come here after seeing it, but is it different?
Ah,▲高嶺＊＊▲... Did you hear that?
It was so cute, so please say it again? Then I'll forget it.
I see, I thought I'd be with you now that we're here.
I'm sorry, I have an errand.
It's okay, I'm happy just to see you.
Yeah, I'm happy too. See ya.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. What are you doing in such a place?
Practicing for a date... I'm kidding. I'm just taking a walk. And you?
I'm also practising for a date.
Oh... I'm sorry, I didn't notice.
In this place. You're kind of absent-minded
I might have been absent- minded, too.
Whassup. Today is a mysterious day.
I met my friends from the girls' club a while ago. Today is a day full of coincidences.
That's going to go on. Maybe you'll see someone after this?
I think it's okay because I've already met the person I want to meet the most... I'm kidding.
Ah,▲高嶺＊＊▲. What are you doing?
I will go in a little while. It's sad to say goodbye after meeting.
That's right. But I could see you with just a glance... I'm kidding. See you.
I'm sorry. I'm in a hurry... Huh?
That is... because you're going to talk like that!
Haha, I'm sorry. But you noticed it.
You can tell by my voice... It's confusing that I didn't notice it right away...
Haha, it's a coincidence. No, maybe fate!?
It's been a hundred years here... I'm kidding.
It was written in the fortune section of a issue there was a good thing this way. It was a hit.
That's good, what about me? Haha.
Huh? What's wrong, you're so surprised...
...I'm sorry. I thought about you, and I was surprised because you suddenly appeared.
I see, I also thought about ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Oh, I'm in good shape. Geez.
▲主人公＊▲. Are you taking a walk?
Actually...I was wandering the city in search of you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲!
I don't believe it. It's not that simple.
▲高嶺＊＊▲? Whassup. You're in a very good mood.
That's because I'm on a date.
That was it... Don't make fun of me.
